---
<section id="index" class="section active relative min-h-screen flex items-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center w-full">
            <div class="text-left order-2 md:order-1">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
                    ANA MARIA<br>POSADA
                </h1>
                
                <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl my-4 font-medium" style="color: var(--primary-color);">
                    Product Designer · UI/UX & Web
                </p>

                <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed md:leading-8 mb-3 font-normal">
                    I turn <strong>creative ideas</strong> into <strong>functional digital products</strong> by
                    blending years of <strong>design experience</strong> with a <strong>love for development</strong>.</p>
                    <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed md:leading-8 mb-5 font-normal">
                    I use <strong>AI tools</strong> to elevate my process and create meaningful, interactive experiences. From <strong>unique brand identities</strong> to <strong>fully developed websites</strong>,I build with intention and care.</p>
                
                
                  
                <a data-section="1" class="primary-btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 explore-btn px-6 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-4">
                    Explore My Work
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket text-lg"></i>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
                <dotlottie-wc 
                    src="https://lottie.host/08cb3a32-e4c4-40f8-854b-851d2988fff8/66Mw3tUnLk.lottie" 
                    speed="1" autoplay loop
                    class="w-[280px] h-[280px] md:w-[450px] md:h-[450px] lg:w-[500px] lg:h-[500px] mx-auto">
                </dotlottie-wc>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="hidden md:block absolute bottom-10 right-10 font-bold animate-pulse"> 
        Scroll to See More → 
    </p>
</section>